<title>CANADA: Provigo to redeem 1st preferred shares.</title>
<headline>Provigo to redeem 1st preferred shares.</headline>
<dateline>MONTREAL 1997-03-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Provigo Inc said on Monday that it would redeem its 3.4 million First Preferred Shares, Series 1 on April 10 for a total of C$85 million.</p>
<p>Provigo will pay C$25 a share, along with a dividend of C$0.05 for the period from April 1 to April 10.</p>
<p>After the redemption date, the company will eliminate its obligation to pay a quarterly dividend of C$0.50 on its first preferred shares, which represent a cost of C$0.07 annually for each common share.</p>
<p>((Reuters Montreal bureau 514-985-2434))</p>
